            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">About the Annual SPIN Meeting</h2>
                <div class="meeting-overview">
                    <div class="overview-text">
                        <p class="lead">Join us for our premier annual gathering where pediatric neuroradiology professionals from around the world come together to share knowledge, explore innovations, and build lasting connections.</p>
                        
                        <p>The SPIN IN-PERSON DUBAI meeting represents the culmination of our fellowship program and serves as the premier educational and networking event for our global community. This intensive three-day program features cutting-edge presentations, interactive workshops, case discussions, and unparalleled networking opportunities.</p>
                        
                        <p>Set against the stunning backdrop of Dubai, this meeting combines world-class education with cultural experiences, making it an unforgettable professional development opportunity.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="overview-highlights">
                        <h3>Meeting Highlights</h3>
                        <ul class="highlights-list">
                            <li>Keynote presentations by world-renowned experts</li>
                            <li>Interactive case-based workshops</li>
                            <li>Fellowship program presentations</li>
                            <li>Research poster sessions</li>
                            <li>Networking receptions and cultural events</li>
                            <li>Industry exhibitions and technology showcases</li>
                            <li>Professional development sessions</li>
                            <li>Global collaboration opportunities</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
